Simple watchface, shows date, battery status, bluetooth and quiet mode. Hands are similar to planets

Hours: red;
Minutes: white;

Bluetooth dot is blue when connected, red when disconnected.

The leftmost dot is red when in quiet mode, green otherwise.

Battery level dots are yellow while charging. A single red dot signals 10% battery remaining.

